# acidrack — the curated boot acid track (song code 0xAC1D5EED) playing its full chain.
# acidrack boots running=true + songmode=true, so it self-plays the arranged track with no
# input — pressing SPACE would STOP it. Deterministic: a clean save-dir → the DEFAULT_SEED song.
# frames 900
# fps 30
# crf 28
